---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Terms of Service | Claim Guardians" 
  description="Terms of Service and legal agreements for using the Claim Guardians website."
>
  <main class="py-20 lg:py-32 section-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-[#082142] mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="italic text-slate-500 mb-12 font-medium">Last Updated: March 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-10 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#082142] mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>By accessing and using the Claim Guardians website, you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provision of this agreement.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#082142] mb-4">2. Professional Representation (Disclaimer)</h2>
          <p>The content provided on the Claim Guardians website is for informational purposes only. Requesting a "Free Claim Review" or submitting information through our web forms does not automatically establish a client-public adjuster relationship. Official representation only begins once a formal contract is signed in accordance with Florida or California state laws.</p>
        </section>
        
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#082142] mb-4">3. No Guarantee of Results</h2>
          <p>While Claim Guardians strives to maximize property damage settlements for our clients, past results do not guarantee future outcomes. Every insurance claim is unique and depends on the specific policy language, cause of loss, and extent of the damage.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#082142] mb-4">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>The website and its original content, features, and functionality are owned by Claim Guardians LLC and are protected by international copyright, trademark, patent, trade secret, and other intellectual property or proprietary rights laws.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#082142] mb-4">5. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>These Terms shall be governed and construed in accordance with the laws of the State of Florida, without regard to its conflict of law provisions.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
